  "texts": [
    "As an example of such a problem, consider climate change, the problem motivating multi-billiondollar investments over the globe.",
    "Minimizing climate change is a very long-term objective.",
    "The lower rank objectives are the development of solar and wind energy and associated grid-level storage and effective energy transport methods, along with the technologies for direct carbon capture.",
    "The even lower rank objectives are the development of cheap, environmentally friendly, and stable chemistries for grid storage.",
    "None of these objectives can be translated into a reward for an experimental campaign."
